ign=\"right\" valign=\"top\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Location</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n<span id=\"DerivedLocale\" class=\"x2\">Menlo Park, CA, US</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"IrcPostingOrgName__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Organization Name</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"IrcPostingOrgName\" class=\"x2\">0001 5008 Trading Systems - Tech</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DepartmentDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">In 1983, the first online trade was placed using early E*TRADE technology.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Today, E*TRADE FINANCIAL is a global financial leader, delivering value and innovation to millions of customers in more than 40 countries worldwide. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><p> </p></span></b></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ul>\n<li>Must be fully conversant with software development life cycle (Agile and Waterfall)</li>\n<li>Deep knowledge and expertise in designing &amp; developing large scale  e-commerce applications</li>\n<li>Candidate must possess excellent verbal and written communication skills and should be able to manage tech meetings, design sessions etc</li>\n<li>Strong hands-on development and troubleshooting skills will be necessary for the position</li>\n<li>Interaction with product management team to understand business and functional requirements and create technical specifications</li>\n<li>Facilitate communication with members of  technical teams, and present in technical working sessions</li>\n<li>Individual contributor position</li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"JobRequirements__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Job Requirements</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"JobRequirements\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ul>\n<li>Bachelor or Master degree in Computer Science</li>\n<li>8+ years of Object-Oriented programming experience in Java &amp; C++</li>\n<li>Experience in building application using Oracle or Sybase.</li>\n<li>Strong knowledge of webservices and REST API</li>\n<li>Extensive experience with SOA implementation</li>\n<li>Strong knowledge of object-oriented programming design patterns and methodologies</li>\n<li>Expertise in both client side and server side technology stacks in a J2EE setting</li>\n<li>Extensive experience in applying open source technologies such as Spring, Hibernate, etc</li>\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a fast-paced environment and meeting tight deadlines</li>\n<li>Strong technical writing, and verbal communication skills</li>\n<li>Ability to understand business problems, and be creative with strong problem solving abilities</li>\n<li>Quick learner , strong team player</li>\n<li>Financial Service industry experience is a plus</li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"AdditionalDetails__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Additional Details</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"AdditionalDetails\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">We offer a competitive and comprehensive benefits package.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Please visit <a href=\"https://us.etrade.com/e/t/career/benefits\"><font color=\"#003399\">https://us.etrade.com/e/t/career/benefits</font></a> to learn more about t