"DepartmentDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">E*TRADE Financial Corporation, the online investing &amp; trading pioneer, with 4.5 million accounts in 40 countries and $110 billion in customer assets, is continuing to reinvent the industry we started.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our unique culture of innovation fosters individual creativity in an environment where you will be continually challenged learning new and exciting technologies.<span style=\"COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></span></p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">SUMMARY:<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">E*TRADE has one of the largest Data Warehouse (Approximately 10 TB) with hundreds of process running every day and millions of transactions. We have highly motivated and dedicated team of 40+ members working towards making it a word class Data Warehouse.<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><p> </p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">The candidate must be a self-starter, who can work under general guidelines in a fast paced work environment.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Previous ETL (Extraction, Transformation, and Loading) experience using IBM Information server 8.x tool will be plus advantage. Experience in any other version of data stage or Other ETL tool is must.<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><p> </p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">RESPONSIBILITIES:<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">Perform technical analysis under the guidance of ETL lead for new projects or any enhancements<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">Participate in a team environme