mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><font size=\"2\">Reporting to the Director of Mareting Campaig Execution &amp; Analytics -- support the Marketing organization with reporting and analytics around performance of Direct Marketing campaigns and promotions</font></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><font size=\"2\">Manage a team of analysts supporting ETrade’s Direct Marketing efforts, including Trading Marketing, Investing Marketing, Bank Marketing, and Corporate Services Marketing teams.</font></span>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><font size=\"2\">Leverage analytics and insight to drive marketing strategy, value propositions and initiatives to help create growth and competitive differentiation</font></span>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"></span><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\">Work with Marketing Managers to understand business objectives of marketing campaigns, and factors for determining success</span></font>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\"></span></font><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\">Create the solution (process &amp; technology) for measuring campaign success</span></font>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\"></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><font size=\"2\">Responsible for data mining, data compilation, data analysis, and data reporting utilizing E*Trade’s data warehouse as well as other relevant data sources</font></span>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"></span><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">Presentation of key findings from campaign analytics </span><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\">in a concise and structured manner to enable effective decision making – distinguish between what management needs to know and what is nice to know</span></font>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\"></span></font><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\">Streamline analytical process by identifying recurring analytical tasks and working with partners to automate</span></font>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\"></span></font><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\">Adhere to existing analytical standards (process, methodology, terminology), and establish new standards where appropriate</span></font>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN\" style=\"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: EN\"></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"><font size=\"2\">Exploratory analytics into a variety of topics to maximize insight into the data, uncover underlying problems, extract important variables, detect anomalies.</font></span>\n</div></li>\n<li><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\">\n<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\"></span><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'\">Work with business and technology partners to establish comprehensive understanding o