UT, US</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"IrcPostingOrgName__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Organization Name</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"IrcPostingOrgName\" class=\"x2\">0014 4032 Relationship Management Call Centers - 0103</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DepartmentDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">In 1983, the first online trade was placed using early E*TRADE technology.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Today, E*TRADE FINANCIAL is a global financial leader, delivering value and innovation to millions of customers in more than 40 countries worldwide. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><p> </p></span></b></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: 197.25pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><font face=\"Arial\"><u><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"></span></u><u><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></u></font> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><b><u><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><font face=\"Arial\">Position Summary:</font></span></u></b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><br><font face=\"Arial\">E*TRADE Client Consultants (CCs) focus on building long-term business relationships with our clients.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>These activities include advising clients on the wide range of investment<span style=\"COLOR: red\"> </span>products and<span style=\"COLOR: red\"> </span>services E*TRADE FINANCIAL offers and recommending solutions that meet their individual financial needs. CCs offer our clients a personal connection to E*TRADE, designed to help them achieve their investment goals.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">   </span>The E*TRADE CC will work with clients to develop an investment plan that meets their personal goals and objectives or provide guidance to help them to be a better investor on their own.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our Client Consultants are ready to make the client experience a great one! <p></p></font></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">Our Client Consultants are self-motivated, independent thinkers who share the common desire to build long-term client relationships. Your ability to achieve success as an E*TRADE Client Consultant is supported by the E*TRADE brand, leadership, marketing support and exceptional training.<p></p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">Upon hire, our Client Consultants are assigned an existing practice of valued clients. As a Client Consultant you will be responsible for the relationship and development of the practice to ensure clients are appropriately considering all the solutions E*TRADE offers.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>You will deepen these relationships by providing investment guidance and advice primarily through phone interactions and face-to-face meetings.  Additionally, you will grow the practice through proactive calls to prospects and client referrals.  To learn more about our client offerings, visit our website: <a title=\"http://www.etrade.com/\" href=\"http://www.etrade.com/\">http://www.etrade.com</a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\"><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><font face=\"Arial\">Responsibilities:<p></p></font></span></u></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><p><span style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: none\"><font face=\"Arial\"> </font></span></p></span></u></b></p>\n<ul style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0in\" type=\"disc\"><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in -27pt 0pt 0in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in\">\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"Arial\">Retain and grow assets of assigned affluent households with significant holdings at E*TRADE FINANCIAL by effectively managing an assigned client base and ensuring that all clients receive a<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">n</span> outstanding client experience.</font></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><p></p></span>\n</li></ul>\n<ul style=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0in\" type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"Arial\">Collect client financial information, analyze and evaluate a client’s financial situation, identify investment objectives, and make investment recommendations through a comprehensive and customized financial planning process.<p></p></font></span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in\"><font face=\"Arial\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Able to reach out to valued E*TRADE clients and prospects to fully explain E*TRADE’s value proposition and deepen relationships through needs based business development efforts</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">.</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><p></p></span></font></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"Arial\">Must be adaptable, flexible and willing to participate in a test and learn environment to determine the quality of new lead campaigns.<p></p></font></span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in\">\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"Arial\">Provide advice on a variety of investment solutions, including advantages and disadvantages to different options, designed to satisfy the client’s specific financial needs.</font></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"> </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><p></p></span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"Arial\">Cultivate current and prospective client relationships and identify opportunities to expand these relationships by responding to client needs with creativity and innovation.<p></p></font></span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"Arial\">Leverage the great client experience that you’ve created for them to ask for referrals to family, friends and business associates.<p></p></font></span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font fa