</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"IrcPostingOrgName__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Organization Name</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"IrcPostingOrgName\" class=\"x2\">1010 2264 Credit - Central Admin</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DepartmentDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">In 1983, the first online trade was placed using early E*TRADE technology.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Today, E*TRADE FINANCIAL is a global financial leader, delivering value and innovation to millions of customers in more than 40 countries worldwide. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><p> </p></span></b></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin\">The Lead Credit Risk analyst is a member of the Credit Risk team within Etrade Bank. The primary purpose of the Credit Risk Analysis team is to mine the whole loan data warehouse for business intelligence related to the loan portfolio, perform customer segmentation and time series analysis, respond to ad hoc inquiries, develop new reporting, automate existing reports and support senior management. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><p> </p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin\">The candidate must be excited about discovering trends in loan data, summarizing and presenting findings, and enhancing existing analytic processes.<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\"><p> </p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\">Job Responsibilities<p></p></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\">The credit risk analyst is responsible for performing:<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri\"><font face=\"Calibri\">Time series analysis on the whole loan portfolios<p></p></font></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri\"><font face=\"Calibri\">Segmentation analysis and profiling<p></p></font></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri\"><font face=\"Calibri\">Customer attrition analysis<p></p></font></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri\"><font face=\"Calibri\">Logistic regression analysis to identify key drivers of customer behavior<p></p></font></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri\"><font face=\"Calibri\">Processing, analyzing, deriving business intelligence from, and reporting on third party vendor data<p></p></font></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal; mso-add-space: auto; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">        