et marketing product management.  This position will have the primary responsibility of developing business requirements, functional specifications and managing product development life cycle for online marketing applications. Candidate must be highly motivated, extremely well organized and have excellent leadership skills. </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #3c3c3c; FONT-FAMILY: \'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\'\"></span></b> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #3c3c3c; FONT-FAMILY: \'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\'\">Responsibilities:</span></b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"><p></p></span></p>\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\">\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #3c3c3c; FONT-FAMILY: \'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\'\">Manage product development of online tools designed to support marketing and client acquisition initiatives.</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"> <p></p></span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\">\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #3c3c3c; FONT-FAMILY: \'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\'\">Coordinate products throughout their lifecycle, from strategic definition to end-of-life planning.</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'\"> <p></p></span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNorm