span class=\"x8\">Location</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n<span id=\"DerivedLocale\" class=\"x2\">Alpharetta, GA, US</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"IrcPostingOrgName__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Organization Name</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"IrcPostingOrgName\" class=\"x2\">0001 2020 Network/Telecom Operations - Shared Services</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DepartmentDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">In 1983, the first online trade was placed using early E*TRADE technology.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Today, E*TRADE FINANCIAL is a global financial leader, delivering value and innovation to millions of customers in more than 40 countries worldwide. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><p> </p></span></b></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span id=\"IRC_VACANCY_VIEW_PAGE\"><span id=\"VacancyDetails\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">The Network Engineer is responsible for contributing network hardware support and design expertise to the centralized market data distribution environment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Provide escalated network support in a high availability, 7x24x365 environment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Work with vendors to configure and support recommended configurations, hardware, and protocols.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Collaborate with network engineering team to ensure consistency and compliance with standards.<span>  </span>Meet on a regular basis with network engineering and operations staff to share knowledge and foster cohesion.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Provide training, monitoring tools, and documentation for turnover to operational staff.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Research new technologies and services as they apply to the market data infrastructure.<span>  </span>Participate in product evaluations and provide technical recommendations.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Evaluate capacity planning requirements as they pertain to networks and protocols.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">          </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Engineer functional designs for new projects and initiatives and present assessments to upper-level management across multiple technical organizations.</span></p></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"JobRequirements__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Job Requirements</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"JobRequirements\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span id=\"VacancyDetails\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">5+ years hands-on experience with enterprise-level routers, switches, and firewalls in a redundant environment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Knowledge and experience with multiple network vendors.<span> </span>Extensive experience designing and configuring all types of Juniper, Cisco, and Voltaire hardware and IOS.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Experience designing WAN environments based on both public and private carrier solutions,such as Frame Relay, point-to-point, T1, DS3, OC3, OC12, OC192, MPLS, VPLS, 10GigE, Infiniband, and encrypted tunnels over public networks.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Strong knowledge of networking protocols such as TCP/IP.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Strong knowledge of routing protocols such RIP, EIGRP, OSPF, and BGP.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Experience with UDP/IP and multicast <span>data </span>technologies such as IGMP, MSDP, PIM SM and DM, RP, BIDIR, PIM</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><span>·<span style=\"FONT: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">         </span></span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">Knowledge of financial feeds and protocols, ie. FIX, OUCH, ITCH, along with Market Data Vendors (MDVs) and ECNs. Experience providing network connectivity to various ECNs and or MDVs</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\">.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 2pt 0in 2pt 0.5in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"