lign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">In 1983, the first online trade was placed using early E*TRADE technology.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Today, E*TRADE FINANCIAL is a global financial leader, delivering value and innovation to millions of customers in more than 40 countries worldwide. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><p> </p></span></b></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">E*TRADE Financial is looking for a product management professional with a strong background in the product management in the Financial Services industry.  This position will be responsible for writing business requirements and functional specifications, as well as managing the product development life cycle for multiple fraud prevention projects simultaneously. Candidate must be highly motivated, extremely well organized, and have excellent communication and time management skills.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"></span> </p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">Responsibilities:<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">* Manage multiple projects on the product development roadmap for products and services designed to identify high risk transactions and mitigate fraud losses<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">* Coordinate products throughout their lifecycle, from strategic definition to end-of-life planning<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">* Gather requirements for projects from various internal teams and translate them into business and functional requirements documents, including visual mock-ups, based on industry knowledge, market research, and customer feedback<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">* Provide subject matter expertise on fraud prevention for various initiatives throughout the organization<p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-FAMILY: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'\">* Interact closely with fraud operations, product, technology development, design, quali