rap><span class=\"x8\">Location</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n<span id=\"DerivedLocale\" class=\"x2\">Alpharetta, GA, US</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"IrcPostingOrgName__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Organization Name</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"IrcPostingOrgName\" class=\"x2\">0040 2357 Consulting - Corporate Services</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DepartmentDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Company Overview</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DepartmentDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">In 1983, the first online trade was placed using early E*TRADE technology.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Today, E*TRADE FINANCIAL is a global financial leader, delivering value and innovation to millions of customers in more than 40 countries worldwide. <?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt\"><b><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><p> </p></span></b></p>\n<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">We are looking for highly energized, dynamic professionals who are ready to join a fast-paced, world leader in the financial services industry. We move at the speed of the Internet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Our work culture fosters an incredible exposure to innovative ideas and challenges that create experience and opportunity.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">Many have risen through the organization to become industry leaders, in both the financial services world and in the community at large.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>E*TRADE is made up of some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry - are you ready to join the industry leader?</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"DetailedDescription__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Detailed Description</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"DetailedDescription\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p>The Consultant participates in client engagements for E*TRADE Consulting.  These projects include business services, financial reporting, technical services, and corporate actions.  Travel may be required to meet and deliver consulting services at Client locations.  The successful candidate possesses a solid understanding of the equity compensation industry and solid technical knowledge in various areas including Equity Edge and financial reporting.</p>\n<p>• Ensure Consulting deliverables of an assigned project are fully met<br>• Written communications and report writing skills<br>• Professional presentation development and delivery skills<br>• Desire to continually learn and stay abreast of industry trends and pending regulatory changes<br>• Continuously enhance Equity Compensation knowledge and expertise.</p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"JobRequirements__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Job Requirements</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"JobRequirements\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">• PC software and web application experience required including MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Access, WebEx<br>• Financial reporting or equity compensation administration<br>• 3 years of client-facing experience in a B2B environment, preferably in the financial services and equity compensation industries<br>• BA/BS preferably in Finance, Accounting or Business Administration<br>• PC software and web application experience required including MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Access, Web-Ex<br>• Certified Equity Professional Level 1-3 preferred<br>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"AdditionalDetails__xc_\">\n<td align=\"right\" valign=\"TOP\" nowrap><span class=\"x8\">Additional Details</span></td>\n<td width=\"12\"></td>\n<td valign=\"TOP\">\n<span id=\"AdditionalDetails\"></span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td height=\"3\"></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt\">We offer a competitive and comprehensive benefits package.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">  </span>Please visit <a href=\"https://us.etrade.com/e/t/career/benefits\"><font color=\"#003399\">https://us.etrade.com/e/t/career/benefits</font></a> to learn more about the opportunities.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><p></p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; COLOR: red\"><p> </p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><spa